QuestData.Title: Grand Theft Telemancy
QuestData.Description:
I'm not opposed to honest competition, $n.
But teleportin' it right out from under our noses leaves me feelin' dirty.
Go teach that thievin' elf what it means t'steal from the Alliance. If they're fightin' dirty, then so will we.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: Teleportation is only fair when we're the ones using it.
QuestData.LogDescription: Slay Third Telemancer Syranel and recover the Breath of Xibala.
